Name: HubSpot - CRM Company Read
Description: Find and Read HubSpot CRM Company Details
Params: company: A description of the company to find - can include things like name, website domain, or Contacts who are associated with it.
Share Tools: github.com/gptscript-ai/tools/apis/hubspot/crm/read
Type: input

#!/bin/env bash

cat << EOF

Use the HubSpot CRM tools to find the company specified within these <input> tags: <input>${COMPANY}</input>.
If the <input>${COMPANY}</input> is empty, refer to your history to select the most relevant company to search for.
Display the company details as well as any additional properties found from the `GetProperty*` tools.

EOF

